{"_response_info":{"status":"ok"},"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/disability-living-allowance-dla-rates.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/disability-living-allowance-dla-rates","title":"Disability Living Allowance (DLA) rates","format":"answer","details":{"need_id":"1886","business_proposition":false,"description":"Disability Living Allowance (DLA) is paid at different rates depending on how your disability affects you","alternative_title":"","body":"\n<div class=\"summary\">\n<p>Disability Living Allowance (<abbr title=\"Disability Living Allowance\">DLA</abbr>) is paid at different rates depending on how your disability affects you.</p>\n</div>\n\n<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Rate</th>\n      <th>Care component</th>\n      <th>Mobility component</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Higher rate</td>\n      <td>£77.45 / week</td>\n      <td>£54.05 / week</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Middle rate</td>\n      <td>£51.85 / week</td>\n      <td>N/A</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Lower rate</td>\n      <td>£20.55 / week</td>\n      <td>£20.55 / week</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p><abbr title=\"Disability Living Allowance\">DLA</abbr> has 2 parts called &lsquo;components&rsquo;:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>care component - if you need supervision or help looking after yourself</li>\n  <li>mobility component - if you can&rsquo;t or find it very hard to walk</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>You could get a combination of both, or just one or the other.</p>\n\n"},"updated_at":"2012-10-22T15:20:37+00:00","tags":[{"title":"Disability benefits","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/benefits%2Fdisability.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Includes Disability Living Allowance, Community Care Grants and Employment and Support Allowance","type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/with_tag.json?tag=benefits%2Fdisability","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/benefits/disability"},"parent":{"title":"Benefits","id":"htt